detail.title: Unfreeze IBC client
detail.description: Due to a relayer crash that exceeded the trusting period, the IBC clients on both nyx chain and gravity-bridge-3 chain are now in a freezed state.\n In order to unfreeze them and continue to benefit from the existing channel between them (which also has a deployed ERC20 contract attached to it), we submit this proposal of updating the existing clients with a fresh new pair of clients.\n This has been tested to work and unfreeze clients, as is also pointed out in the Cosmos SDK documentation: https://github.com/cosmos/cosmos-sdk/blob/master/docs/ibc/proposals.md
